Portland, Oregon is a city that is known for being "weird".  This word means that people there are different and like to do things that are not normal. Some people like this about Portland. They think it is fun and creative.  

Portland has many things to see and do. There are many stores and places to eat. People enjoy going to concerts and watching sports.  There are also many parks and gardens.

Some people think that Portland is becoming too normal. They say that more people from California are moving there, and the city is changing. But Portland is still a place where people are free to be themselves. 

There are many ways to be weird. Some people like to wear strange clothes. Other people like to do unusual things, like yoga with goats. Portland is a place where people can be different and be accepted for who they are.

The mountains are always there. They are in the north. They see the sun each day. I forget about them sometimes. I am busy with work and life. But they are there. They do not change. They do not care about my problems. When I am worried, the mountains show me I must look at them. When I look at them, I feel better. I feel stronger.

I came here when I went to school. The mountains north of the school were very beautiful. The school has pretty buildings, ponds, and trees. But the mountains are the most beautiful. The town is nice too. There are many places to get coffee. You can walk to the center of town. There are old buildings there. The town feels old. But it is also busy.

After a few blocks, you can go back to the quiet town. You can go past the library. There are two kinds of places close together. This makes the town special. It is fun to explore. I have many memories here. I walked with friends after studying all night. We went to the movies in the fancy theater.

The town also has sad memories. The ponds are good for thinking. I have cried there at night when I was sad. I watched the turtles, ducks, and bugs. I thought about my life. What is my purpose? I walked past the ponds, the park, and the houses.

The sun came up. I saw the mountains. They were big and strong. They touched the sky. They made me feel strong too.

Bensonhurst is in Brooklyn. It is easy to find. Public transport is good. Many people use it. Bensonhurst is in the city. It feels like New York City. Many Asian stores are there. Many Asian people live in Bensonhurst now. 

You see Asian stores on every block. Supermarkets and wash places are very popular. People like them. The food is good. The prices are low. It is easy to get there. There are four supermarkets near me.

Bensonhurst has people from many places.  There are immigrants and their children. Many big stores are owned by Asian people. There is a park near my home. It has basketball courts, a big field, and a playground. The park is for everyone.

There are not many big buildings in Bensonhurst. People live in houses or apartments. Most houses are for two families. The people are kind but loud. Cars make a lot of noise. It can be loud at night.

Bensonhurst is safe, but be careful at night. Some people may be mean. I was hurt by someone in the past. People steal packages too.

People do not always clean up after their dogs. You may see dog waste on the ground. Watch out!

My home is on a big hill. It is the biggest hill in my area. People call it the "work out hill" because many runners go up it. There are no sidewalks on my street. People walk on the road. The road is bad in some places. It is hard to drive on. Some wires are old and broken. It rains a lot. The rain hurts the wires. They look bad. There are many tall trees. People do not like the trees. They cut down many trees. They want to see the ocean. Many houses are high up on the hill. They have big windows. You can see the ocean from the windows. The ocean is beautiful at sunset. The sky is orange. It is often cloudy. The sun is not bright. It rains a lot. Moss grows on everything. My car was green with moss once. I had to clean it.

There are not many children in my area. There is a school nearby. There are many old people. People have dogs. The dogs run around. They go into houses. I had a dog in my house once. There are rabbits. They dig in gardens. My cats hunt rabbits. There are birds. There are small birds and big birds. There are no stores nearby. There are restaurants by the water. They sell food from the sea. There is a beach, but it is small. There are rocks by the water. You can throw rocks in the water. The water is not wide. You can see the other side.

I live in a small town in Tennessee. It is a calm place. My street is small and has two big roads on each side. Many cars go on my street. I see the same people every day. We know each other well. 

Many people work in their yards. In winter, we go sledding. We live at the start of the street. We see all the cars that go by. If we see a new car, we pay attention. Some neighbors walk for exercise. Kids ride bikes. We are home often because we work from home. 

There are four of us: my wife, me, and our two daughters. They are eleven and fourteen. We go outside often. We play in the rain sometimes. We grill outside on our back porch. It smells good. 

Many people cut their grass. We hear the sound of lawnmowers often. There are many trees. We rake the leaves in the fall. It smells good when the leaves burn. I like fall. This year, we have not had much winter.

Our garage is at the back of our house. We do not use the front door much. I like to work in the garage. When the garage door is open, I feel close to the neighborhood. 

Holidays are quiet. Thanksgiving is busy. Many people visit. It is the same for Mother's Day and Christmas.

I like living here. It is a good place.

My home is in the desert. The desert is dry. There is dirt everywhere. People who have not lived here do not know how the desert feels. The desert is brown. Green grass is rare. People who have grass spend much money to keep it. When I first lived here in the nineteen ninety's, houses were far apart. Now, there are more houses. The place looks more like a city. But most places are changing like this. People here are friendly. Like in every place, there are good parts and bad parts. I live near old people. It is a nice place. Stores here are big chains, like Food for Less and Smart and Final. If you want special food, you must travel. I do not see Whole Foods here. 

Most people in my city work in construction. This is because there is still much open space. This worries me. I like things the way they are. I came from a big city and I do not want to go back. I work in construction. I install drywall and T-bar.

I like the animals here. People come to the desert for many reasons. The desert is beautiful. The desert is dry and has many different animals. People should learn about these animals to live with them safely. My family likes the animals. My three children like lizards and bugs.

Victorville is a good place to visit. There are things to do. The San Bernardino County Fair is fun. You can also visit Wrightwood to see the snow and go skiing. The Victor Valley Museum has rocks, bones, old things, and stories about the city.

My home is the college campus. I live in a dormitory. My friends are my neighbors. My school has homes, stores, and a park.

There are many kinds of homes on campus. Some are apartments. Two to four people live in each room. There are four to six rooms on each floor. Many people live in each apartment building.

Some homes are houses. These are for teachers and older students.

Dormitories are for students. Two students share a room.

My school has many different people. Students come from many places. Teachers live in the houses. Newer students live in the dormitories. Older students live in the apartments.

The school has many stores. There are places to eat. There is a store that sells school clothes. There is a store where students can buy food.

The school has a park. It is a safe place for everyone.

I have lived here for ten years. When I first came, I was sad. I moved from Riverdale to Stockbridge. My family wanted a better place to live.  There is good housing and a good high school here.  It took time to get used to the new place. I made new friends and new enemies at school. I did not know my neighbors well except for Mr. Glen and his children, and Dennis. Mr. Glen and his family are nice. I think of them like family. I went to Mr. Glen's wedding. It was fun. I hope to have a wedding like that one day. Mr. Glen's wife, Ms. Veda, threw a strap from her leg. I caught it! I did not catch the flowers. We all danced. I danced with Marsharii, one of Mr. Glen's daughters.  I hope she is doing well.

Our neighborhood is like a maze. I use a GPS to find my way. I like to explore. I have gone to the park with my friends Kason and Curtis. We play video games and have fun. I like to go to the park. It is peaceful. I like to walk there and bring sticks to practice my balance. I also bring my bokken, a wooden sword. 

There is a basketball court and a tennis court in the neighborhood. I do not play basketball or tennis much now, but it is nice to have them there. My dad taught me and my friend to play tennis with Mr. Graves. We had a lot of fun.  I have had a lot of fun in this neighborhood. I have many stories. I think the best is yet to come!

My home is near my college. I like living here. There are mostly apartment buildings. There are a few good, cheap restaurants and bars. One bar changed name. It is more expensive, but the drinks are okay. Most people here are college students or have little money. There are many children here. There is a school near my apartment. I do not know my neighbors. They smoke a lot of marijuana. The building put an air freshener near their door. My boyfriend and I thought this was funny.

The buildings around me are old. Some have new insides. There are new apartments down the street. They look bad. They are expensive, but the rent is high because they are near the college. There is a cheap restaurant near me. They serve food on paper plates. They use a microwave. There is a gas station across the street. It may not be a good place to work. The road was fixed last summer. Now there is a good sidewalk. There are trees and grass.

My apartment building is near trees. There are more trees here than down the street. There is a line of trees behind my building. I live on 42nd street. Behind me is 43rd street. It is not as nice. The sidewalks are bad. The buildings look old. There are many trees here. I think they hide the buildings.

There is a lot of crime near here. It mostly happens in one apartment building, but other apartments have problems too. I like where I live. It is affordable. There are good places nearby. I like that the college is close. There are buses to the store and downtown.

My house is in a small place. Many houses are the same. They are yellow with white steps and green roofs. Most people know each other. We talk in the street when the small children play. It is nice to be out of doors. It feels old-time. We see trees, fields and clouds. It is good. But, last night, we had a bad storm. We heard the warning. I went to the bathroom with my small dog, my bag and pillows. My big dog stayed in the living room. It was very loud. We heard big hail on the ground. The road was hot. The hail made steam. The sun came out and it rained. A rainbow appeared. I took pictures. My friends liked them. The storm went away. People came home. Everything was normal. I like this place. I moved here from another state. I like the way people talk. My house has two rooms and two bathrooms. All the houses look the same. But the inside is different. Some are small. I like to walk in the big field. I see deer. I hear a big frog. It is good to live here. It is near a big city, but it is quiet. I hear roosters in the morning. It is like a small village. I like my home.

I move to this place when I start eighth grade. It hard to make new friends at first. But I make friends with two boys. One lives two houses away. The other lives on my street. They not live here now, but I remember them. Many people who lived here when I arrive still live here. My neighborhood like other American neighborhoods. It has many two-story houses. I hear kids play outside every weekend. My neighborhood quiet most days. I have no problems with the people here. People leave you alone unless you need help. I order many things online. I never have a package taken from my porch. I trust my neighbors. There is a park near my house. I have good memories there. I play basketball, football, and baseball with the other boys. I also have a bad memory there. I get hit in the nose playing football. But the good times better. Now I take my cousin's children to the park. They small and like to play on swings and slides. The park make me think of the past. My neighborhood has many kinds of people. There is many food. You can find Chinese, Indian, Mexican, and Italian food nearby. Many people use apps to get food, like GrubHub and DoorDash. Fast food is popular, but you can find it anywhere. There are many pizza places too. The stores have everything you need. There are dry cleaners, a Walgreens, a CVS, and a Jewel-Osco grocery store. There is even an Indian store. I like my neighborhood. I am happy here.

My home town is small. It is in South Carolina. It is not very big, but it is important for farmers. The town is called Johnston. People say it is the best place for peaches. There are many peach trees. There are also many cows.

Most homes are far apart. They are two stories tall. Some have metal roofs to keep cool in the summer. Some have gray roofs. The homes are far from the road so people can grow things there.

In the center of town, there is one light. There are a few stores there. There are three places to eat fast food: Hong Kong (a small Chinese place), Fiesta (Mexican food), and Gary's (burgers). There used to be a pizza place, but it closed.

There is a small drug store called Maxwell and Halford. They are known for their Cherry Coca-Cola. There is also a small grocery store called IGA. People often go to a bigger store in a nearby town for most of their food. The most popular store is Dollar General. It sells many things and is always busy.

There is a furniture store called Possibilities. A kind woman runs it. It has been in town for a long time. They even have people to deliver the furniture.

There is a pet store next to the furniture store. It is called Clark's Cuts and Kennels. They take care of pets.

The doctor and the vet are not in the center of town. They have small offices, but they are good doctors.

There is one elementary school. After fifth grade, children go to school in the next town.

There are no parks in town, but they are building one.

There are not many things to do in town. There are no movie theaters or bowling alleys.

It is a nice town, but it is very small. You could drive through it and not even notice!

I first heard about my house on a talk show. It was about people who went missing. It was a small shock. Most places to live here cost more than one thousand dollars each month. I had not heard this story. My friends had not heard it either. Maybe it is the hard times. I know some of my friends cry at night. Things are expensive, but we know how to save money. You begin to like old toys from the market and clothes that have been stored. You smell less as an adult. You might smoke, or you might just get used to things. But the market is always there. The smell of being an adult is old magazines on a closed piano. It gets in the leather and stays there even after you wash it. There are three places to buy used things near here. If you start on one side, you can go to two places that give things to charity, a library, a store that sells old books, and a store that sells old things.

The city center is very busy. Cars and people fill the streets each morning, but you do not hear it in the stores. No matter how many people or cars pass, the stores are quiet. It is a good place to spend an afternoon. Each year, there are more cars and people. It is a growing city, they say. It has one of the biggest online businesses for buying and selling things. It is still growing. It reminds me of New York. Everyone has their own goals, and no one asks much from you. You can be alone, quiet, and independent, and people will leave you alone. It is not like the South, where being a little worried means you care. People here do not ask about your life. You can be quiet as long as you like, and the city will move on like waves on the beach. It is a lively place to be. 

There is always something happening. The pianist next door and the two people who sing upstairs make music. We are more like a community of friends than a building of strangers. We come together for our needs, birthdays, funerals, and to help each other. I am lucky to be here. I like most of my neighbors, and they are good to me. I clean up after myself and share food, and they do the same. I bring them their mail, and they bring mine. It is nice to see them, and I think they enjoy my company as much as I enjoy theirs. I live in a big, impersonal building, but it is people like my neighbors that make me feel like I did not make a big mistake with my life.

I live in a suburb. It is like many other suburbs. There is a homeowner's association. All the houses look the same. They are small and have two car garages. The yards are short with grass and rocks. There are some small trees. The roads are new. They are in good shape. 

Most houses are one story, but some are two stories. We do not have mailboxes in front of each house. There are big boxes at the end of the street. Everyone has a key for their box.

My house is on the edge of the city. It is part suburb, part country. There are many pools and walking trails. People can swim or walk. 

Many people in my neighborhood are old. It is a safe place. There are also some middle-aged and young people.

The city is big, but it feels small. We have a mall. It is not big, but it has many stores.

I can drive to many stores in fifteen minutes. We have good stores with food and cheap stores.

My neighborhood is good. It is safe and well kept.

I live in a small town. It is near a big city. My house is on the east side of town. This side is not rich. Many people here have low jobs. The houses are old. Most people rent them.  But the people here are nice. They say hello when I walk by. There is some crime here, but not much. A few years ago, a man was shot near my house. My neighbor’s son was shot at a bar. It is sad. People here take drugs. Many people die. There are groups to help people stop taking drugs. This town is good in some ways. My son goes to a good school. The teachers are nice. My son has special needs, but he is not bullied. The school gives food to children who need it.  The town is making the town look better. They fixed the roads and parks. But they fix the west side more, not the east side. People here do not like this. I like living here. People are nice. The school is good. There are stores to buy things. My house is not expensive, but it is good. We have lived here a long time. We like it here.

My house is in a place with much culture. It is on a hill. Old buildings are around it. They have history. I live in a tall building. It has seven stories. It is across from an old theater. Down the street is a small bar. People go there in warm weather. They wait in line to get in.

A big park is near my house. It is not far from the street. Tall steps go up the side of the park. In winter, people who do not have homes sleep in tents. They put the tents close together. They are warm in the city. They can walk to a place where they can shower.

I like my city. I like the people. Hilltop was bad a long time ago. Gangs were bad there. People talk about the police trying to stop the gangs. People remember. They work hard to keep their city clean. They care about their home.

Some people say that white people should not walk at night. I think this is old thinking. I am dark. Maybe people see me as one of them. Hilltop is real. People live there. They show it. They give help. They see me. I know that the city is not perfect. People are not perfect. But Hilltop feels like home.

I live in a small town in Michigan. There are farms and small cities. There are no big stores like Walmart or Target. You must drive to go anywhere. But my town is very pretty. It has two lakes: Lake Michigan and Lake Charlevoix. There are beaches everywhere. My neighborhood is small. Houses are not close together. They are old and different. Many have full basements. Houses have yards with trampolines, gardens, and sometimes animals.  People work hard. They raise families. Children play outside. People walk dogs and ride bikes. Neighbors know each other. People wave and smile. Lawns are kept neat. There are no piles of leaves. The grass is short. Plants are trimmed. My neighborhood is not fancy, but it is good for families. It is quiet and safe. You can walk to the sheriff’s office, the health department, and the recycling center. There are baseball fields and an airport nearby. You can hear planes taking off and landing. You can walk to get ice cream. My children can bike to the park. It is a good place to live.
